{"id": 2619, "genre": 1001, "title": "今年哪些小事让你有“一个时代开始/结束”的感觉？", "description": "我们心中的“时代背景板”，都是由哪些碎片组成的？（题图来自：iStock ©️ Grandfailure）", "record_count": 6937, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181113144739uIBAWvEjC8MoXzqK.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-12-14T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 316672, "content": "国家开始补贴就业", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057898}, {"id": 316928, "content": "毛衣战...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879167}, {"id": 316673, "content": "公司开始纷纷裁员", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057898}, {"id": 316929, "content": "乐坛，这个时代我面对的是烂大街的歌曲。以前的经典歌曲真的能熬过时间。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1532602}, {"id": 316674, "content": "5g来临，基因编辑婴儿诞生，一代大师的离世……", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371145}, {"id": 316930, "content": "考完四级", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1527907}, {"id": 317955, "content": "为钱犯愁了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1535986}, {"id": 316932, "content": "钱包只有卡，没有钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1532621}, {"id": 316677, "content": "越来越多我们这个时代的名人去世", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528022}, {"id": 316933, "content": "行业巨头的陨落，比如手机，比如照相机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 547590}, {"id": 316678, "content": "人事调整，让我觉得就过了一年，真快。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531744}, {"id": 316934, "content": "00后的出现", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1046495}, {"id": 316679, "content": "平成年代结束", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276336}, {"id": 316935, "content": "霍金挂了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723325}, {"id": 316936, "content": "开始关心父母、带自己的老师及好朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1397170}, {"id": 317960, "content": "斯坦李去世", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497726}, {"id": 316937, "content": "和男朋友聊的话题越来越现实和沉重了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1532630}, {"id": 317449, "content": "莫德里奇拿金球奖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1404450}, {"id": 318473, "content": "之前很多免费的东西都开始付费模式了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475516}, {"id": 317451, "content": "看不懂微博热搜，自我感觉老了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1495478}, {"id": 317707, "content": "我感觉是妇联已经拍了10年了吧，我已经成年了👀", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514737}, {"id": 316684, "content": "生活大爆炸要完结了", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 533504}, {"id": 316940, "content": "梅西已经到职业生涯晚期了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531905}, {"id": 316685, "content": "开始被催找对象了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911131}, {"id": 316941, "content": "18岁一过 每天的时间抓都抓不住", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1532644}, {"id": 316686, "content": "今年好多人去世，5G时代即将来临。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1344132}, {"id": 316943, "content": "人工智能的到来", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991356}, {"id": 316944, "content": "广东文理分科的最后一届", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498661}, {"id": 316689, "content": "我在中兴N系安卓机开始了切水果的征程，朋友们还在死守塞班。当时有一种直觉 世界通讯业要变化了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132806}, {"id": 316945, "content": "毕业两年了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1307555}, {"id": 316690, "content": "最后一节课下课的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496928}, {"id": 316946, "content": "特朗普当选", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753653}, {"id": 318994, "content": "金庸去世.李咏去世.二月河去世.", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1499484}, {"id": 316691, "content": "满身伤痛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 617245}, {"id": 316947, "content": "今年毕业，无忧无虑的日子永远也不会有了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359635}, {"id": 316692, "content": "和我同龄的买了别墅，结了婚生了娃。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396508}, {"id": 316693, "content": "一年级的小朋友不玩“你拍一，我拍一”了，而玩的是什么“阿里巴巴”", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 817014}, {"id": 316949, "content": "BAT开启时代", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1532720}, {"id": 316694, "content": "好听的歌怎么都是小时候听过的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 69, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531846}, {"id": 316695, "content": "苹果都出到xs了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531855}, {"id": 317719, "content": "我挣钱了彡(￣_￣；)彡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 854923}, {"id": 318231, "content": "我开始不用QQ空间和朋友圈了，不看也不发", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416657}, {"id": 316696, "content": "即将大学毕业", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879075}, {"id": 316952, "content": "重拾阅读 在阅读中汲取智慧 在生活中体验人生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461581}, {"id": 318744, "content": "开始重新流行穿汉服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1300119}, {"id": 316697, "content": "2018年过完，学生时代彻底告别。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1494933}, {"id": 316953, "content": "李敖大师去世了，对于文人一个时代结束了 。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1526763}, {"id": 316698, "content": "以前看变形计都是和我一样的90后，现在都是00后的小弟弟，瞬间感觉自己老了。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531862}, {"id": 316700, "content": "很多小时候喜欢的人物去世。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513949}, {"id": 316956, "content": "立宪。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462606}]}